name: Magical Lamp
description: Surrealistrasyon//Şerif Gümüşbaş//Digital Art//3000x3000 pixel//It's pretty hard in the world to feel like a magic stardust that is part of a magic universe. Mankind has filled this planet with dozens of strangeness that distracts from this feeling. Maybe that's why we've been getting more and more interested in space in the last century//Drawing is an impressive form of expression for me with its universal and differentiating structure for each viewer.
